"docs":{},"h":{"docs":{},"i":{"docs":{},"s":{"docs":{},",":{"docs":{"deploy.html":{"ref":"deploy.html","tf":0.007936507936507936}}}}}}},"u":{"docs":{},"p":{"docs":{"deploy.html":{"ref":"deploy.html","tf":0.023809523809523808}},"l":{"docs":{},"o":{"docs":{},"a":{"docs":{},"d":{"docs":{"deploy.html":{"ref":"deploy.html","tf":0.007936507936507936}}}}}}}},"v":{"docs":{},"i":{"docs":{},"s":{"docs":{},"i":{"docs":{},"b":{"docs":{},"l":{"docs":{"deploy.html":{"ref":"deploy.html","tf":0.007936507936507936}}}}}}}}},"length":85},"corpusTokens":["'~/.npm_global'","(optional)",".npm_global","/usr/local/lib",":)","anyth","broken","build","bunch","call","chang","cli","clone","commit","config","congrat","creat","deploy","deploy.sh","dev","don't","environ","first","folder","follow","fuck","g","gitbook","github","haven't","home","https://github.com/optativa/optativa.github.io","https://github.com/optativa/optawiki_dev","initi","insid","inspect","instal","introduct","latest","locally.","locat","made","make","manag","modifi","move","need","now.","npm","obvious","on","onc","optativa","optatiwiki_dev","optawiki_dev","packag","page","pages,","please.","prefer","prefix","preview","readmes,","repositori","run","script","see","serve,","set","setup","step","sure","this,","up","upload","visibl","want","whatev","wiki","wiki'","write"],"pipeline":["stopWordFilter","stemmer"]},"store":{"./":{"url":"./","title":"Introduction","keywords":"","body":"Optativa wiki page\nJust write about whatever the fuck you want\n"},"deploy.html":{"url":"deploy.html","title":"Setup","keywords":"","body":"Setting up your wiki dev environment\nInitial setup\n\nIf you don't have it install npm with your preferred package manager\nInstall gitbook by running npm install -g gitbook-cli\n(Optional) npm might want to write in /usr/local/lib obviously don't do\nthis, create a folder for npm in your home called .npm_global and then\ncall npm config set prefix '~/.npm_global'\nClone the dev repository located at https://github.com/Optativa/optawiki_dev\nAlso clone the github page repository https://github.com/Optativa/Optativa.github.io\n\nCongrats you should be set up to modify these pages\nModifying your first page\nIf you inspect optatiwiki_dev you should see a bunch of readmes, these are\nthe ones that make up the wiki's pages, you can modify them as you please.\nIf you want to preview your changes you need to run gitbook build followed\nby gitbook serve, this will let you preview the wiki locally.\nOnce you have made all the changes you wanted move to the deploy step\nDeploying\n\nFirst make sure you have commited all your changes to optawiki_dev\nRun gitbook build to get the latest build of the wiki\nMake sure you haven't broken anything :)\nRun the deploy script that should be inside optawiki_dev called\ndeploy.sh\nFollow the deploy script steps\n\nCongrats your page should be uploaded and visible now.\n"}}}